bsg.npolar.no/pop-maps.htm" class="external text" title="http://pbsg.npolar.no/pop-maps.htm" rel="nofollow">population status reviews</a> and <a href="http://pbsg.npolar.no/status-table14.htm" class="external text" title="http://pbsg.npolar.no/status-table14.htm" rel="nofollow">Table 1</a> summarizing polar bear population status per 2005.</li>
