<li id="cite_note-campbell-22">^ <a href="#cite_ref-campbell_22-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-campbell_22-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-campbell_22-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-campbell_22-3" title=""><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-campbell_22-4" title=""><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-campbell_22-5" title=""><sup><i><b>f</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-campbell_22-6" title=""><sup><i><b>g</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-campbell_22-7" title=""><sup><i><b>h</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-campbell_22-8" title=""><sup><i><b>i</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-campbell_22-9" title=""><sup><i><b>j</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-campbell_22-10" title=""><sup><i><b>k</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="news" id="CITEREFCampbellLunau.2C_Kate2008">Campbell, Colin; Lunau, Kate (2008-01-25). "<a href="http://www.macleans.ca/science/environment/article.jsp?content=20080123_5242_5242&amp;page=1" class="external text" title="http://www.macleans.ca/science/environment/article.jsp?content=20080123_5242_5242&amp;page=1" rel="nofollow">The war over the polar bear: Who's telling the truth about the fate of a Canadian icon?</a>". <i>Maclean's</i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.macleans.ca/science/environment/article.jsp?content=20080123_5242_5242&amp;page=1" class="external free" title="http://www.macleans.ca/science/environment/article.jsp?content=20080123_5242_5242&amp;page=1" rel="nofollow">http://www.macleans.ca/science/environment/article.jsp?content=20080123_5242_5242&amp;page=1</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-03-09</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=The+war+over+the+polar+bear%3A+Who%27s+telling+the+truth+about+the+fate+of+a+Canadian+icon