ocher%2C+Andrew+E.&amp;rft.date=Fall+2007&amp;rft.volume=1&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=24%E2%80%9327%2C+43&amp;rft.place=Lawrence%2C+Kansas&amp;rft.pub=The+Wildlife+Society&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.biology.ualberta.ca%2Ffaculty%2Fandrew_derocher%2Fuploads%2Fabstracts%2FStirling_Derocher_Wildlife_Professional_PB_climate_2007.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Polar_bear"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>.</li>
